r1.name: Brooke Lillard
r1.text: Mr.Harper came out the same day we called him. He had our drain fixed in no time and was very reasonably priced! Will be recommending to friends and family members!

r2.name: Kevin Hamilton
r2.text: Mr.. Harper is great man. I called with  a problem and he was able to give me some help over the phone to help me out!  If that didnt work he was gonna come and do the job at a great price. He was nice enough to try to save me some money and gave me a couple of ideas over the phone and it worked. Will be my first call for any future plumbing problems in the future!

r3.name: Alexandria Lopez
r3.text: Our toilet was not flushing. I was pregnant with no working toilet. Imagine that. Very good Christian man who came out on a Sunday to do the job. Friendly service with affordable pricing. Hands down the best plumber.

r4.name: Shelbi Andrews
r4.text: Harper?s Drain Cleaning is the person to call. On Memorial Day weekend, he came on a Sunday to help us. He is honest, professional and very reasonably priced. We are so happy we called them!

r5.name: Coleman James
r5.text: Harper?s Drain Cleaning awesome service. Chris was there for us and kept the city on their toes with their part. He continuously kept coming out to see if the city did their part that way he could help us with the issues on our end. Great customer service and very polite and respectful and great affordable pricing!

r6.name: Tasha Ray
r6.text: Great and friendly service, showed up in a timely manner, and had us fixed up pretty quickly.

r7.name: Dianna Willie
r7.text: Absolutley Great Service. Friendly and Resonably Price. My Mom uses him alot

r8.name: Michelle Easton
r8.text: We always receive fast, friendly and excellent service. I highly recommend Harper's Drain Cleaning.

r9.name: Wendell Tolson
r9.text: Work was done immediately and perfect. Chris followed up to make sure everything was working. Awesome service!!

r10.name: Bobby Turner
r10.text: When our bathtub stopped draining, we called Mr Harper and he was at our house in less than 30 minutes, and had fixed the problem in less than an hour.  Would highly recommend.

r11.name: Donna Mullen
r11.text: Great Job! Very affordable! Showed up exactly when he said he would. Got my issue figured out and resolved it quickly. Explained how to keep from having any reoccurring issues. Thank you again!

r12.name: Heather Palmer
r12.text: Cannot say enough good things about the team! Will never use anyone else! Honest and genuine people who care about getting their customers taken care of!
